# free

Free the IOHIDInterface object.

## Declaration

```swift
virtual void free(); 
```

## Overview

Release all resources that were previously allocated, then call super::free() to propagate the call to our superclass.

## Miscellaneous

- **init**: Initialize an IOHIDInterface object.
- **matchPropertyTable**: Called by the provider during a match
- **start**: Start up the driver using the given provider.
